Part 5.  Contact Information, Declaration, and Signature of the Person Preparing this Application, If Other Than the Applicant.  Preparer's Signature.  8. A. Preparer's Signature. This signature field can not be signed with a digital signature and the signee's name can not be typewritten into this space. This is a protected field. Print and sign in ink.
